queries.sql: SELECT COUNT(*) as total FROM participants WHERE program_id = '3' AND DATE(created_at) = CURDATE()
SELECT COUNT(*) as total FROM participants WHERE program_id = '3' AND ref_code_ambassador IS NOT NULL AND ref_code_ambassador != ''
SELECT DATE(created_at) AS date, DATE_FORMAT(created_at, "%b %d, %Y") AS label, COUNT(*) AS total FROM participants WHERE program_id = '3' GROUP BY DATE(created_at) ORDER BY date DESC LIMIT 30

SELECT CASE WHEN gender IS NULL OR gender = '' THEN 'Not Specified' ELSE gender END AS gender, COUNT(*) AS total FROM participants WHERE program_id = '3' GROUP BY CASE WHEN gender IS NULL OR gender = '' THEN 'Not Specified' ELSE gender END ORDER BY total DESC

SELECT CASE WHEN nationality IS NULL OR nationality = '' THEN 'Not Specified' ELSE nationality END AS nationality, COUNT(*) AS total FROM participants WHERE program_id = '3' GROUP BY CASE WHEN nationality IS NULL OR nationality = '' THEN 'Not Specified' ELSE nationality END ORDER BY total DESC LIMIT 10

SELECT CASE WHEN TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, birthdate, CURDATE()) < 18 THEN 'Under 18' WHEN TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, birthdate, CURDATE()) BETWEEN 18 AND 24 THEN '18-24' WHEN TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, birthdate, CURDATE()) BETWEEN 25 AND 34 THEN '25-34' WHEN TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, birthdate, CURDATE()) BETWEEN 35 AND 44 THEN '35-44' WHEN TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, birthdate, CURDATE()) BETWEEN 45 AND 54 THEN '45-54' WHEN TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, birthdate, CURDATE()) >= 55 THEN '55+' ELSE 'Unknown' END AS age_group, COUNT(*) AS total FROM participants WHERE program_id = '3' AND birthdate IS NOT NULL GROUP BY age_group ORDER BY FIELD(age_group, 'Under 18', '18-24', '25-34', '35-44', '45-54', '55+', 'Unknown')

SELECT a.name AS ambassador_name, COUNT(p.id) AS total_referrals FROM ambassadors a LEFT JOIN participants p ON a.ref_code = p.ref_code_ambassador AND p.program_id = '3' WHERE a.program_id = '3' GROUP BY a.id ORDER BY total_referrals DESC LIMIT 5
